Activity Diary allows to record a diary for for your activities. You can categorize them and get a reminder for recurrent actions.

This app is currently under development and not yet feature complete. Do not use in a productive environment and expect your data to be lost on version upgrade. Please be patient or contribute on https://github.com/ramack/ActivityDiary and submit bug reports, feature requests and pull requests!

